ygData.messageBody:
Greetings fellow creatures of Norrath. Just introducing myself. I have been playing EverQuest since June of 2002. Can't really say that this game is easy, I have had some problems (for instance dying in every zone). But I guess you have to live and learn. I don't know many secrets about the game, but just throw basically any topic at me and I will comment on it. But for now just introducing myself.

Kryptorchid Kinderfield

Necromancer
